[06/05/2018 13:18:01] <font color="#00ff00">Los empresarios</font>
[06/05/2018 13:18:01] <font color="#00ff00">Sandro Silva y Marta Seco</font>
[06/05/2018 13:18:02] <font color="#00ff00">son todo un fenómeno</font>
